###########
# INSTALL #
###########

Agora needs several Python packages that can all be installed with pip.
They are listed in requirements.txt:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Once all these install ok just run:

bash ./checkAgoraIntegrity.sh

to check the install of AGORA.

Once everything is ok, go to doc/HowTo.pdf to learn how to use AGORA.
